620
00:34:13,280 --> 00:34:15,449
We even don't know who did it.

621
00:34:15,450 --> 00:34:18,109
Well, Commandery Prince An is not in Chang'an now.

622
00:34:18,110 --> 00:34:22,180
Is there no judge who can arrest criminals?

623
00:34:24,070 --> 00:34:28,569
Your Majesty, these officials are incompetent.

624
00:34:28,569 --> 00:34:32,839
You can denounce them and punish them as you want.

625
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:38,249
You don't have to save face for them and make yourself feel bad.

626
00:34:38,250 --> 00:34:41,519
Your Majesty, getting angry can hurt your health.

627
00:34:41,520 --> 00:34:45,009
You must take care of yourself.

628
00:34:45,010 --> 00:34:51,479
Your Majesty, you have been busy with national affairs recently.

629
00:34:51,480 --> 00:34:55,410
Have a cup of soothing tea first.

630
00:35:21,190 --> 00:35:25,949
Master, when it comes to making the emperor happy,

631
00:35:25,949 --> 00:35:27,979
