632
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:30,700
No one can do it better than you do.

633
00:35:33,170 --> 00:35:40,810
Listen. Only when I am happy, I'll have the mood to make him happy.

634
00:35:41,610 --> 00:35:44,309
Well, Master, what are you happy about?

635
00:35:44,309 --> 00:35:48,109
Tell me and let me share your happiness.

636
00:35:48,110 --> 00:35:51,030
What else could it be?

637
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:55,379
Zhou Han finally did a good job.

638
00:35:55,380 --> 00:35:58,580
Shouldn't I be happy about it?

